    "name": "刃狱",
    "steam_appid": 2340210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战场上的舞蹈，节奏控场大师</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅需 <strong>轻击｜重击｜冲刺</strong> 三键，衍生数十种连招组合，灵活施展，七进七出驰骋沙场。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的技能设计</strong>：在冲刺结束<strong>前</strong>按下 <strong>轻击｜重击</strong>，既可延续闪避免受打击，又能立即施展还击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>远近攻击</strong>：重击突进，轻击快刀，战场瞬息万变，玩家可自由应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>反弹远程攻击</strong>：将敌人的远程攻击反弹回去，攻守易形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精准反击</strong>：当敌人出手时也是暴露弱点的时候，在这瞬间还击，可取得高额伤害</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样破敌方式</strong>：即使是Boss也可以寻找路径进行偷袭，难度直接减半。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可通过资源管理，运用各种飞斧辅助杀敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>纯粹法则</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无装备/无成长，强度只由操作决定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多级难度可选，兼顾新手体验与硬核挑战。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>敌人生态</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尸潮狂潮</strong>：在废弃城镇、荒野教堂、冰封湖底等多场景中，用冲刺走位制造血肉走廊。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行与强攻</strong>：大部分敌人可背刺秒杀，精英敌人也可偷袭扣半血，自由选择战斗风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑夜模式</strong>：提升敌人强度与战斗收益，难度越高，回报越丰厚。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索与操作</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开放世界设计</strong>：线性关卡与自由探索并存，隐藏区域通往未知宝藏与试炼。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操作优化</strong>：支持手柄、键鼠及单键盘操作（WASD移动+JKL战斗），键位自定义自由度拉满。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>慎入声明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ 需要装备Build/开放建造/剧情驱动的玩家请绕行。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发者的话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这是三年淬炼的动作熔炉——<br>每个技能手感调试超百次，每场对战皆为精心设计的操作课题。<br>没有怜悯，只有最纯粹的刀锋对话。”</p>",
